'''Kevnis''' (klass: Arachnida, urdh: Araneae) yw [[Melldrosek|melldrosogyon]] owth anella ayr. I a's teves eth garr, ha dens lymm hag a skitya venim. Meur anedha a wra owrlin. An ethgarrogyon yw seythves yn niver a eghen a bub urdh enevales<ref>Sebastin PA & KV Peter (''ed'') 2009. ''Spiders of India''. Universities Press. ISBN 978-81-7371-641-6</ref>. A-dro dhe 48,000 eghen a gevnis, ha 120 teyluyow re beu kovadhys gans taksonomiedhyon<ref>Platnick, Norman I. (2009). "[http://research.amnh.org/entomology/spiders/catalog/COUNTS.html The World Spider Catalog, version 9.5]". American Museum of Natural History. Retrieved 2009-04-25.</ref>. Moy ages ugens klassans re beu profys a-ban 1900<ref>Foelix, Rainer F. 1996. ''Biology of spiders''. Oxford University Press. ISBN <bdi>0-19-509593-6</bdi>.</ref>. Kevnis a vew war bub brastir a-der an Antarktek, hag yn ogas ha pub bewva a-der ayr ha'n mor.

